==English==
===Etymology===
Compare French ''[[:fr:granulaire|granulaire]]''. See [[granule]]

===Adjective===
#Consisting of, or resembling, grains; as, a granular substance. Granular limestone, crystalline limestone, or marble, having a granular structure. 

